      <hedline>
        <hl1>My Name Is Not Robert</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Virginia White letter on Benjamin Weiser's August 6 article notes almost no one involved cared about plight of wrongly imprisoned Kerry Sanders (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I don't know which is worse -- the fact that Sanders spent two years in a maximum security prison for a crime he didn't commit, or the fact that almost no one involved gave a damn.</p>
        <p>Virginia White  Charlottesville, Va.</p>
      </block>
